summary:
•Senior project manager with >20 year experience in high tech engineering and project management roles. 
•Able to cross borders, while keeping focus on the project goals, continuously searching for consistency and commitment.
•Bringing  worlds together: Mechatronics - IoT - Connectiviy - Diagnostics -Security/Privacy & Safety
•Passion for pioneering and new challenges. Not afraid of ambiguous situations because of confidence, focus and resilience.
•Personal characteristics:  analytical, pragmatic, solution-oriented and involved. Straightforward and result driven. 
•I like to be challenged and to support experienced professionals with my expertise; to set the direction and to guide them. I value honesty and learning opportunities by receiving and giving direct feedback. 
•Used to work in complex situations with multi-disciplinary teams and various cultures. Able to adapt, to think creatively, to understand dynamics relative to type and level of clients and relations. 
•Fluent in Dutch (native), English and German (professional level).
